examples.en: She found him sitting alone, deep in meditation.
Daily meditation helps clear his mind.
Prayer and meditation helped her put her mundane worries aside.
She uses meditation as a way of reducing stress.
Chant is often used as a form of meditation and prayer.
Meditation involves focusing the mind on a single object or word.
She spent the morning in meditation.
Meditation allows you to enter a state of deep relaxation.
The habit of meditation is the basis for all real knowledge.
